checkout this link, to understand the logic here: 
http://www.anewmorning.com/2009/04/21/programming-your-own-chat-bot-the-logic/

to compile, link the boost regex library:
http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_49_0/libs/regex/doc/html

currently regex is implemented.
checkout the .bcf files to see how to add/edit how the bot responds.
the regex dll needs to be in the execution directory.
